<h2>Welcome to the Airbnb Data Dashboard</h2>

<!-- Brief description of the dashboard -->
<p>Explore and analyze Airbnb properties with ease using this interactive dashboard. Here, you can view all property listings, search by property ID or name, and filter results based on specific criteria.</p>

<h3>Features of the Dashboard</h3>
<ul>
  <!-- Feature 1: View all properties -->
  <li><strong>View All Properties:</strong> See the full dataset in a clean, sortable table format with property images for quick reference.</li>

  <!-- Feature 2: Search and filter properties -->
  <li><strong>Search and Filter:</strong> Easily find properties by ID, name, neighbourhood, or room type, with results displayed instantly.</li>

  <!-- Feature 3: Load more functionality for better performance -->
  <li><strong>Load More Functionality:</strong> Avoid long page loads by fetching data in chunks, while still having the option to explore all properties.</li>

  <!-- Feature 4: Detailed property view -->
  <li><strong>Detailed Property View:</strong> Access comprehensive information about each property, including host details, pricing, minimum nights, and more.</li>

  <!-- Feature 5: Responsive design -->
  <li><strong>Responsive Design:</strong> Works seamlessly on both desktop and mobile devices for convenient access anywhere.</li>
</ul>

<h3>About This Project</h3>
<!-- Short project description -->
<p>This application is developed as part of a hands-on assignment to demonstrate skills in web development, data handling, and dynamic front-end interactions. It uses Node.js, Express, Handlebars, and JavaScript to create a fully interactive experience for exploring real-world Airbnb datasets.</p>
